   <text>
      <body>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_1.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <p>
            <seg rend="left">
               <hi rend="latintype">via <hi rend="underline">
                     <placeName ref="K00554">Brindisi</placeName>
                  </hi>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <seg rend="right">
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00525">Hamburg</placeName>
                  <date when="1872-01-11">11 Januar 1872</date>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <lb/>
            <seg rend="center">Herren <hi rend="latintype">
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. Kniffler &amp; C<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>
                  </orgName>
                  <lb/>
                  <hi rend="underline">
                     <placeName ref="K00525">Yokohama</placeName>
                  </hi>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <lb/> Meine ergebenen Zeilen vom<lb/>
            <date when="1872-01-03">3 <choice>
                  <abbr>
                     <hi rend="latintype">d. Mts</hi>
                  </abbr>
                  <expan> dieses Monats</expan>
               </choice>
            </date> höfl bestätigend bekenne ich mich<lb/> zum Empfange Ihrer geehrten
                Zuschrift<lb/> v <date when="1871-11-22">22 <hi rend="latintype">Novbr</hi>
            </date> &amp; bemerke ich mir gern den<lb/>
                Verkauf der 2¢ <hi rend="latintype">gelb <term type="goods" ref="K01528">Tuch</term> à <term type="currency" ref="K01508">$</term>
               <measure type="currency" quantity="2.2" unit="mex$">2<hi rend="superscript">20</hi>
               </measure> ⅌ yd,</hi>
            <lb/> welcher hoffentlich in Ordnung gehen wird.<lb/> Für Ihre ferneren märktlichen
                Berichten<lb/> danke ich Ihnen bestens &amp; hoffe daß es<lb/> Ihnen inzwischen
                gelungen ist die<lb/> 100 <hi rend="latintype">
               <unclear>Stg</unclear> assorted Cloth</hi> sowie auch die<lb/>
            <hi rend="latintype">grey mixed</hi> lohnend zu begeben, zumal<lb/> da weitere
                Sendungen in diesen Qualitäten<lb/> in Vorbereitung sind.<lb/> Mit dem Abschlusse
                der Bücher<lb/> beschäftigt, beehre ich mich Ihnen unter<lb/> der Falte Auszug Ihrer
                vorjährigen<lb/> Rechnung mit dem Ersuchen zu behändigen<lb/> dieselben <choice>
               <abbr>gefl</abbr>
               <expan> gefällig</expan>
            </choice> prüfen + wenn in Ordnung<lb/> befunden den <hi rend="latintype">Saldo
                    de</hi>
            <lb/>
            <add style="transformRotateZ(-45deg)" resp="other" place="marginLeft">
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <hi rend="underline">richtig</hi>
               </hi>
            </add>
            <seg rend="center">
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <hi rend="underline">
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Bp</abbr>
                        <expan cert="medium">Britische Pfund</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <measure type="currency" quantity="3598.2">3598,2</measure>
                  </hi> ⅌<hi rend="underline">
                     <date when="1872-01-01">1 Januar 1872</date>
                  </hi>
               </hi> zu</seg>
            <lb/> meinen Gunsten, gleichmäßig auf neue<lb/> Rechnung vortragen zu lassen.<lb/>
                Ich erlaube mir Copie des <choice>
               <abbr>
                  <hi rend="latintype">Cto Crt</hi>
                  <lb/>
               </abbr>
               <expan> Conto Corrent</expan>
            </choice>
            <lb/>
            <add style="transformRotateZ(-45deg)" resp="writer" place="marginLeft">
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <hi rend="underline">2 <choice>
                        <abbr>Cto Crti</abbr>
                        <expan> Conti Correnti</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </hi>
               </hi>
            </add>
         </p>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p> Ihres <choice>
               <abbr>
                  <hi rend="superscript">w</hi>/</abbr>
               <expan> werten </expan>
            </choice>
            <hi rend="latintype">
               <placeName ref="K00545">Hiogo</placeName>
            </hi> Hauses mit <hi rend="latintype">Saldo</hi> von<lb/>
            <add style="transformRotateZ(-45deg)" resp="other" place="marginLeft">
               <hi rend="underline">Fehlen noch<lb/>Particulars<lb/> ex <placeName ref="K00545">Hiogo</placeName>
               </hi>
            </add>
            <seg rend="center">
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Bp.</abbr>
                     <expan cert="medium">Britische Pfund</expan>
                  </choice>
                  <measure type="currency" quantity="1029.1">1029„ 10</measure> + <unclear>Rwen</unclear>
                  <measure type="currency" quantity="20692.24" unit="unclear">20,692„24„</measure> ⅌ <date when="1872-01-01">1
                            Janr <choice>
                        <abbr>a c.</abbr>
                        <expan>anni currentis</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </date>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <lb/> beizufügen + grüße Sie, in Erwartung<lb/> Ihrer angenehmen Berichte<lb/>
            <seg rend="right">mit Hochachtung<lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <hi rend="underline">
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01064">H. C. Bock</orgName>
                  </hi>
               </hi>
            </seg>
         </p>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_4.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <p>
            <seg rend="center">
               <stamp style="round" type="postal">
                  <placeName ref="K00509">HONG KONG</placeName>
                  <lb/>C<lb/>
                  <date when="1872-02-23">FE 23<lb/>
                     <unclear>72</unclear>
                  </date>
               </stamp>
               <lb/>
               <lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">via <placeName ref="K00554">Brindisi</placeName>
               </hi>
               <stamp style="rectangular" type="postal">P. D. </stamp>
               <stamp style="round" type="postal">
                  <placeName ref="K00522">HAMBURG</placeName>
                  <lb/>
                  <date when="1872-01-11">II/I<lb/>72</date>
                  <lb/>N I-2N 1.</stamp>
               <lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">Messrs<lb/>
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. Kniffler&amp; C<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>
                  </orgName>
               </hi>
               <lb/>
               <add style="textOrientation: straight" resp="unclear">
                  <unclear>Hm</unclear>
               </add>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00525">Yokohama</placeName>
               </hi>
               <lb/>
               <stamp style="round" type="postal">
                  <placeName ref="K00525">YOKOHAMA</placeName>
                  <lb/>A<lb/>MR I<lb/>72</stamp>
            </seg>
            <lb/>
            <add style="writingMode: vertical-lr; textOrientation: sideways-right" resp="other" place="marginRight">1872<lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00522">Hamburg</placeName>
                  <date when="1872-01-11">11 Jan.</date>
                  <lb/>
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01064">H. C. Bock</orgName>
                  <lb/>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>R</abbr>
                     <expan>Received</expan>
                  </choice>
                  <hi rend="underline">
                     <date when="1872-03-05">5 März</date>
                  </hi>
                  <lb/>
                  <date when="1872-03-25">25 Marz</date>
               </hi>
            </add>
         </p>
      </body>
   </text>
   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_1.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <p>via Brindisi<lb/> Hamburg, 11th January 1872<lb/>Messrs. L. Kniffler &amp;
                Co.<lb/>Yokohama<lb/>Politely confirming my respectful lines from <lb/>the 3rd of
                this month, I acknowledge <lb/>receiving your esteemed letter from <lb/>22nd
                November &amp; gladly note the <lb/>sale of the 2¢ yellow cloth at $ 220 ⅌
                yd,<lb/>which will hopefully go well. <lb/>I give you my warmest thanks for your
                <lb/>further market reports &amp; hope that you <lb/>have by now managed to sell at
                a <lb/>profit the 100 pieces[?] of assorted cloth <lb/>as well as the mixed grey,
                especially as<lb/>further shipments at these qualities are <lb/>being prepared.
                <lb/>Being busy with balancing the books, <lb/>I have the honour of supplying you
                <lb/>with the enclosed statement of your account <lb/>for last year with the request
                kindly <lb/>to check this + if found to be correct <lb/>to carry forward the balance
                of<lb/>⟨correct⟩Bp 3598,2 ⅌1st January 1872, <lb/>in my favour, uniformly on new
                <lb/>account. <lb/>I am taking the liberty of enclosing a copy of the <lb/>⟨2
                current account⟩</p>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>current account of your esteemed Hiogo house with a balance of <lb/>⟨Particulars
                still missing <lb/>ex Hiogo⟩Bp. 1029„ 10 + Rwen 20,692„24„ ⅌ 1st Jan of this
                year<lb/>+ send you my greetings, in anticipation <lb/>of your pleasant reports
                <lb/>Yours respectfully <lb/>H. C. Bock</p>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1872_01_11_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_H_C_Bock_Hamburg_4.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <p>HONG KONG<lb/>C<lb/>FE 23<lb/>72[?] <lb/>
            <lb/>via BrindiseP. D. HAMBURG<lb/>II/I<lb/>72<lb/>N I-2N 1.<lb/>Messrs.<lb/>L.
                Kniffler&amp; Co.<lb/>⟨Hm⟩Yokohama<lb/>YOKOHAMA<lb/>A<lb/>MR
                I<lb/>72<lb/>⟨1872<lb/>Hamburg 11th Jan.<lb/>H. C. Bock <lb/>R[eceived] 5 March
                <lb/>25th March⟩</p>
      </body>
